    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="805268442">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-805268442" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-805268442" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="805268442">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/miktvxq/">木。</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-09-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">八个故事里面的每个主人公都对某种物质特别迷恋或者某种习性特别执着 难道“正常人”就没有忧伤可讲么 如果是我 我想我会从一个比较正常的角度去写</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="810950743">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-810950743" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-810950743" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="810950743">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chenanqi/">螺丝帽</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar10 rating" title="很差"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">8.1他妈哪来的？翻第一页男主就开始“尝”女主的五官，还“你的味道挺正的”，作者嗑药了还是开挂了？！靠写知音漫客去吧，8.1到底他妈哪来的？！</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="660082567">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-660082567" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-660082567" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="660082567">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/jessicazt/">Summer</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-04-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">今天下午在pageone书店站着看完的。。。非常不错，风格很像伊恩的《最初的爱情，最后的仪式》，荒诞离奇孤独却又贴近人性，看完心里有种怪怪的感觉，就像当初看完《最》一样，说不出道不明</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="692509252">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-692509252" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-692509252" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="692509252">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linpeiyuan/">林培源</a>
                    <span>2013-06-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">鲁敏总是在写“畸凌”人，但是这个先例已经有乔伊斯、舍伍德·安德森、奈保尔开创了，她想在这里写当下中国的“暗疾”，写不为人知的隐秘，可是，为什么读了一遍，我就不想再读了？</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="846881435">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-846881435" class="vote-count">0</span>
